{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"isNaN 函數","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_925b2d10050621507a9c990cb803dcca","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"onlyinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<h4 id=\"isnan_函數\">isNaN 函數</h4>\n<p><code>isNaN</code> 函數對參數求值，來判斷是不是〝NaN〞（不是數字，not a number）。<code>isNaN</code> 的語句如下︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">isNaN(testValue)\n</pre>\n<p>此處的 <code>testValue</code> 就是你想要求值的值。</p>\n<p><code>parseFloat</code> 和 <code>parseInt</code> 函數會在求出來的值不是數字的時候返回〝NaN〞<span style=\"font-family: monospace;\">。</span>如果傳入的是〝NaN〞，<code>isNaN</code> 返回 true，否則為 false。</p>\n<p>以下的代碼會對 <code>floatValue</code> 求值，來判斷這是不是數字，然後呼叫相應的程序︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">floatValue=parseFloat(toFloat)\n\nif (isNaN(floatValue)) {\n   notFloat()\n} else {\n   isFloat()\n}\n</pre>\n</div>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/isFinite_函數\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/parseInt_和_parseFloat_函數\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"isNaN 函數對參數求值，來判斷是不是〝NaN〞（不是數字，not a number）。isNaN 的語句如下︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Functions","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_925b2d10050621507a9c990cb803dcca","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_925b2d10050621507a9c990cb803dcca/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_925b2d10050621507a9c990cb803dcca","title":"isNaN 函數"}],"pageTitle":"isNaN 函數 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}